---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Research | Frédéric Bouchard">
  <section class="page-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="kicker">Research</div>
      <h1>Research</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        My research focuses on ultrafast quantum photonics: using short optical pulses, temporal modes, and nonlinear optics to process quantum information at high rates.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container grid two">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Ultrafast photonic quantum circuits</h3>
        <p>
          We develop programmable optical circuits based on temporal encoding, enabling compact and passively stable approaches to quantum information processing.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Telecom nonlinear quantum optics</h3>
        <p>
          We study quantum frequency translation, Kerr switching, squeezing, and photon-number-state manipulation in fiber-compatible wavelength bands.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Quantum measurement</h3>
        <p>
          We work on high-speed measurement schemes including photon-number-resolving detection, homodyne-style measurements, and ultrafast tomography.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Quantum networks and interconnects</h3>
        <p>
          We explore photonic components and protocols that could support high-rate quantum communication and quantum networking.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
